<table>
<tr>
<td>
<h3>Connecting to the Data and R Scripts</h3>
<p>
The nodes in the DDG retain connections to the scientific data,
  the R scripts and plots produced.  By clicking on nodes in the DDG,
  the user can see the values as they existed at that point in the
  computation.
</p>

<p>DDG Explorer requires Java 1.7.</p>
</td>
<td>
<img src="figures/Plot.png" align="right" width="434"
	height="367"> 
</td>
